stream = StringIO()
adb = ADB(stream)
adb.run_cmd('LOAD 00 00 04; LOAD 01 01 F4; MUL 00 01 02')
adb.run_cmd('eval 2')
assert adb.vm.counter == 10
assert adb.vm.registers[0] == 4 and adb.vm.registers[1] == 500
assert adb.vm.registers[2] == 0
adb.run_cmd('eval 1')
assert adb.vm.registers[2] == 2000
